  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>

        <div xml:id="Kali18-kilavi">
          <p type="edition">iḵtu “oṉṟāt tamariṉum” (to.po.41) eṉṉuñ cūttirattil “nāḷatu ciṉmaiyu miḷamaiya 
            tarumaiyun - tāḷāṇ pakkamun takutiyatamaitiyu - miṉmaiya tiḷivu muṭaimaiya tuyarcciyu - maṉpiṉa 
            takalamu makaṟciya tarumaiyum” eṉak kūṟiya eṭṭiṉaiyun talaivaṉ kūṟak kēṭṭa tōḻi avaṟṟai 
            “nikaḻntatu kūṟi nilaiyalun tiṇaiyē” (to.po.44) eṉṉum vitiyāṟ ṟalaivaṟkuk kūṟic 
            celavaḻuṅkuvittatu.</p>
          <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"></p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="Kali18">
            <lg type="edition">
                <l>arumporuḷ vēṭkaiyi ṉuḷḷan turappap</l>
                <l>pirintuṟai cūḻāti yaiya virumpinī</l>
                <l>yeṉṟō ḷeḻutiya toyyilum yāḻaniṉ</l>
                <l>maintuṭai mārpiṟ cuṇaṅku niṉaittukkāṇ</l>
                <l>ceṉṟōr mukappap poruḷuṅ kiṭavā</l>
                <l>toḻintava rellāru muṇṇātuñ cellā</l>
                <l>riḷamaiyuṅ kāmamu mōrāṅkup peṟṟār</l>
                <l>vaḷamai viḻaitakka tuṇṭō vuḷanā</l>
                <l>ḷorōokai tammuṭ ṭaḻīi yorōokai</l>
                <l>yoṉṟaṉkū ṟāṭai yuṭuppavarē yāyiṉu</l>
                <l>moṉṟiṉār vāḻkkaiyē vāḻkkai yaritarō</l>
                <l>ceṉṟa viḷamai taraṟku.</l>
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                <l></l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
